NAME
    Perinci::CmdLine::Lite::Patch::DumpMeta - Patch Perinci::CmdLine::Lite's
    action_call() to dump meta first

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of
    Perinci::CmdLine::Lite::Patch::DumpMeta (from Perl distribution
    Perinci-CmdLine-Lite-Patch-DumpMeta), released on 2018-12-07.

SYNOPSIS
     % PERL5OPT=-MPerinci::CmdLine::Lite::Patch::DumpMeta yourscript.pl ...

DESCRIPTION
    This patch can be used for debugging. It wraps action_call() to dump
    Rinci metadata first.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Perinci-CmdLine-Lite-Patch-DumpMeta>.

SOURCE
